snippet.title: Kingdom Rush Alliance is NOW AVAILABLE!
snippet.description:
It's good that you made it this far... Kingdom Rush 5: Alliance is FINALLY HERE! Time to lead the Linireans and Dark Army shoulder-to-shoulder into the ultimate battle. Rush to your Store and join the adventure now! 📱 Android: https://bit.ly/android_kralliance 📱 App Store: https://apple.co/46dpC35 💻 Steam: https://bit.ly/steam_kralliance
